data.description: Large family home built in 2017 with 4 bedrooms (one could be used as a bonus room OR 2nd primary suite) plus a main level office, formal dining room, eat-in kitchen and bar area seating in kitchen, ALL on a 3/4 acre lot with mountain views! Large walk-in custom closets in all bedrooms, walk in pantry, half covered and half open deck on back and covered porch on front of house with professional landscaping. Laundry on upper level with bedrooms. New paint throughout and no carpet in the house.All of this with the convenient location of being less that 5 minutes from daycare, school, gym, and churches!
